                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Lance célère"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Compétence élémentaire</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 2 pts de </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">DGT Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> et crée une </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">barrière brûlante</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Barrière brûlante</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">État de déploiement</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Accorde </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">1 pt de</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">bouclier</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> à votre personnage actif.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">(Peut être cumulé, 3 pts maximum)</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/03/35653081/375c5e00af78c34af064565c8c932329_23251200142265590.png",
                "id": "talent38829",
                "key": "Bénédiction flamboyante",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Bénédiction flamboyante"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Déchaînement élémentaire</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 2 pts de</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">DGT Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">et</span> <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">crée une</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">barrière brûlante</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> et un </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">o-yoroi embrasé</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Barrière brûlante</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">État de déploiement</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Accorde </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">1 pt de</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">bouclier</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> à votre personnage actif.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">(Peut être cumulé, 3 pts maximum)</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">O-yoroi embrasé</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">État de déploiement</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Lorsque votre personnage a utilisé une attaque normale :</span> <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 1 pt de</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">DGT Pyro</span> <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">et crée </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">une barrière brûlante</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nombre d'utilisations : 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/03/35653081/47b82b01f63f39b206ba0c985d5de119_1774204334760323171.png",
                "id": "talent75368",
                "key": "O-yoroi écarlate",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "O-yoroi écarlate"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Applique l'élément Pyro et peut déclencher les réactions élémentaires :</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Fonte </span>: <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">DGT actuels +2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Évaporation </span>: <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">DGT actuels +2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Électro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Surcharge </span>: <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">DGT actuels +2 et bascule de force la cible pour le personnage suivant</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Brûlure </span>: <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">DGT actuels +1 et crée une </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">flamme brûlante</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> qui inflige des DGT Pyro à la fin de la manche (Utilisable 1 fois, 2 cumuls maximum)</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/03/35653081/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_7662837451180020058.png",
                "id": "talent49973",
                "key": "DGT Pyro",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "DGT Pyro"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">DGT physiques</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Les DGT physiques n'appliquent aucun élément et ne peuvent pas non plus déclencher de réactions élémentaires.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Bouclier</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Un bouclier qui absorbe les DGT reçus par le personnage qu'il protège.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Nombre d'utilisation</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Après le déclenchement de l'effet de cette carte, 1 de ses </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">utilisations </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">est consommée.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Une carte est immédiatement défaussée une fois toutes ses </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">utilisations </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">épuisées.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/03/35653081/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_4206517440478899061.png",
